# Testing

- Always run tests yourself rather than asking the user to run them.
- Use `make test` to run the full test suite (it runs `uv run pytest -v`).
- To run a single test: `uv run pytest tests/<file>::<class>::<test> -x -v`
- Tests require macOS with calendar access granted. `make test` has the necessary permissions.
